-- Citigroup Appoints Pankaj Vaish as Bank's Head of Markets for South Asia
-- Abhay Singh
-- 2010-07-15T15:22:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/citigroup-appoints-pankaj-vaish-as-bank-s-head-of-markets-for-south-asia.html

          
          
             Citigroup Inc. appointed Pankaj
Vaish as head of markets, South Asia, the New York-based company
said in a statement.  
 Vaish was previously managing director and head of equities
at Nomura Securities, the statement said.  
          
          


  


        